snippet.textDisplay:
The covers or remakes I loved from this season:

Episode 1:
Ali Sethi - Ranjish Hi Sahi

Episode 2:
Junoon Ft RFAK, Ali Noor - Sayonee
Kaavish, Quratulain Balouch - Faasle
Ali Zafar - Jaan-e-Bahaaraan 

Episode 3:
Sahir Ali Bagga, Aima Baig - Baazi

Episode 4:
Javed Bashir, Akbar Ali Ft Aamir Zaki - Naina Moray

Episode 5:
Attaullah Esakhelvi, Sanwal Esakhelvi - Sab Maya Hai
RFAK - Rangrez

Episode 6:
Umair Jaswal, Jabar Abbas - Dam Mast Qalandar (This one is less favourite as compared to other ones, just felt that this type of vocal style has been covered so many times, it could've been differently amazing)

Episode 7: 
Sajjad Ali - Tera Naam (Don't know but it does sound like the old Pakistani song Tera Naam Hatheli' to me. However a beautiful song).
Shuja Haider, Aima Baig - Baanware (Mostly because of Shuja Haider's voice chords)
